{"tid":2452482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公民涉洗錢被引渡至美國 北韓宣布與馬來西亞斷交","createTime":"2021-03-19T00:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T01:19:27.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3f54e6fb5237b8368cba7c56bff4813c8995c7","tid":2452482,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:50:00.000Z","msg":"北韓今日（3/19)宣布與馬來西亞斷絕外交關係，原因是一名北韓公民被引渡到美國。<br />\n<br />\n北韓周五在官媒朝中社發表的聲明中寫道，馬來西亞17日犯下不可饒恕的罪刑，強行把無辜的北韓公民送至美國。因此北韓外交部在此宣布與馬來西亞徹底斷絕外交關係，聲明還抨擊馬來西亞屈服於美國的壓力，對北韓採取敵對行為。<br />\n<br />\n而聲明中把這名未透露姓名的人，描述為在新加坡從事合法對外貿易活動，堅稱說他參與非法洗錢是捏造的。<br />\n<br />\n被引渡的北韓公民名叫文哲明（Mun Chol Myong，音譯）和家人在馬來西亞生活10年久，2013年至2018年，文哲明透過在新加坡任職的貿易公司和偽造文件，購買奢侈品運返北韓，違反聯合國制裁令。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210319/IUTCS3FSOJAWFIWCEY5G7AXVCA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FIUTCS3FSOJAWFIWCEY5G7AXVCA%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=ce49cded\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FIUTCS3FSOJAWFIWCEY5G7AXVCA%2F&h=eafc4057\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210319/IUTCS3FSOJAWFIWCEY5G7AXVCA/</a>"},{"pid":"3f388c9baac48f1311447ecdb0649259d79e3f94","tid":2452482,"uid":141268,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:04:28.000Z","msg":"北韓駐馬來外交官：我唔想番去啊"},{"pid":"01945eadde113247e28057f38df5b09239c37cd4","tid":2452482,"uid":214502,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:08:17.000Z","msg":"點睇個北韓人都唔會想返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a97a36bd429002705504d05d778b0b09ba4c77","tid":2452482,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞想同你建交咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14aaa25cfd54d66f4b3673768406c95b83f8fdb","tid":2452482,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:14:45.000Z","msg":"引渡 X<br />\n營救 O"},{"pid":"7cb2d0cb605a7cfdb4210714ba335b19d4848589","tid":2452482,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"依d國家建交黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a260033f3fc5bec9fb6744fcb0a2f58b5620614b","tid":2452482,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:19:27.000Z","msg":"孟晚周國幾時同楓葉國斷交？"}]}